sourcesContent: import React from 'react' import axios from 'axios'; import { Link } from 'react-router-dom' function GreffierShow({nom, date, adresse, etat, nombre, payement, cin, tel, cnss, contrat, sexe, actif, ID, OnDelete}) { return ( {nom} {date} {adresse} {etat} {nombre} {payement} {cin} {tel} {cnss} {contrat} {sexe} {actif} OnDelete(ID)}> ) } export default GreffierShow ;
